de.feu.showgo.ui.dialogs

Class ShowGoSaveFileChooser

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.feu.showgo.ui.dialogs.ShowGoSaveFileChooser

  • public class ShowGoSaveFileChooser
extends java.lang.Object
    A customized JFileChooser save dialog. The class displays a JFileDialog that asks for confirmation on saving a file if it already exists. The dialog only accepts .showgo files.
